CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 5, 1941, pg. 14, reads: "Kay Club Boys Off On Bicycle Jaunt - Pictured above are the boys who went on the Kay Club's novel bicycle jaunt to Highland Park last week. The boys visited the zoo and other interesting places. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Eleven boys, including two with signs on bikes inscribed "Don't Hit Me, Kay Boy's Club Bicycle Hike," and two men, posed with bicycles on sidewalk
